<br>
High damage melees represent the largest threat to me, thus a stacking DS of the fire pet may be nice against a rogue or a monk that is dual wielding, but most of the big threats come from 2Handers (monk shovel, paly/sk/war 2handers) so a DS isn't quite as attractive. As such, I'd keep myself DSed as it is and use the extra hps to pet kite them around as needed.<br>
